==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Grossness
<hw>Gross"ness</hw>, <pos>n.</pos> <def>The state or quality of being
gross; thickness; corpulence; coarseness; shamefulness.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><q>Abhor the swinish <qex>grossness</qex> that delights to wound the'
ear of delicacy.</q> <rj><qau>Dr. T. Dwight. </qau></rj>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Grossular</ent>⟦br⟧
